<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Message Sent - NEXCORE</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&family=Rajdhani:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #03060a;
    --accent: #00f0ff;
    --accent2: #a855f7;
    --text: #e4f1ff;
    --muted: #4a6580;
    --success: #00ff88;
    --neon-glow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,240,255,0.5);
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
  }
  .container {
    max-width: 600px;
  }
  .success-icon {
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    border: 3px solid var(--success);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 60px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0,255,136,0.3);
    animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0,255,136,0.3); }
    50% { box-shadow: 0 0 50px rgba(0,255,136,0.5); }
  }
  h1 {
    font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 6vw, 48px);
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--success);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,255,136,0.5);
  }
  p {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 18px 40px;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: var(--bg);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    clip-path: polygon(15px 0, 100% 0, 100% calc(100% - 15px), calc(100% - 15px) 100%, 0 100%, 0 15px);
  }
  .btn:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(0,240,255,0.4);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  .info {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,240,255,0.2);
    background: rgba(0,240,255,0.03);
  }
  .info-title {
    font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .info-text {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="success-icon">✓</div>
    <h1>Message Sent!</h1>
    <p>Thank you for contacting NEXCORE Support. We've received your message and will respond within 24 hours.</p>
    <a href="/" class="btn">← Return to Homepage</a>
    <div class="info">
      <div class="info-title">What happens next?</div>
      <div class="info-text">Check your email inbox (and spam folder) for our response. We typically reply within 2-4 hours during business hours.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>